<appendix id="app.terminology">
      <title>Terminology</title>
      <para>
    Because multiple spellings of a variety of words and terms are in common
    usage, we have standardized on a variant to use in our documentation.
    Terms in this table are capitalized as they would be in the middle of a
    sentence. Some words listed here are provided because they are often
    written incorrectly by non-native speakers.
  </para>
      <para>Note that only some of the most important SUSE products are listed here.
    If the product you are documenting is not listed, please refer to the
    Marketing department or the SUSE homepage, <ulink url="http://www.suse.com"/>.
  </para>
